<h1>Descripci&oacute;n del programa</h1>
<strong><strong>C&oacute;digo SNIES:</strong> </strong>1537<strong><br />Bogot&aacute;<br />Formaci&oacute;n Universitaria: </strong>Pregrado<br /><strong>Modalidad: </strong>Presencial<strong><br />T&iacute;tulo: </strong>Fil&oacute;sofo (a)<br /> <strong>Duraci&oacute;n: </strong>8 semestres<br /> <strong>N&uacute;mero de cr&eacute;ditos:</strong> 126<br /> <strong>Jornada: </strong>Diurna<br />Ver programa completo <a href="https://filosofia.uniandes.edu.co/images/pdfs/Cursos_Filo201720ok.pdf">aqu&iacute;</a>
